《'''思悼'''》（{{lang-ko|'''사도'''}}，{{lang-en|'''The Throne'''}}）是一部於2014年7月8日拍攝<ref>{{cite web|title=Song Kang Ho and Yoo Ah In's New Film ''Sado'' Holds First Shooting|url=http://www.soompi.com/2014/07/18/song-kang-ho-and-yoo-ah-ins-new-film-sado-holds-first-shooting/|accessdate=24 July 2014|date=18 July 2014|website=[[Soompi|Soompi]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140719032450/http://www.soompi.com/2014/07/18/song-kang-ho-and-yoo-ah-ins-new-film-sado-holds-first-shooting/|archive-date=2014-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2015年9月16日上映的韓國歷史電影，由[[宋康昊|宋康昊]]、[[劉亞仁|劉亞仁]]、[[文瑾瑩|文瑾瑩]]主演；[[李濬益|李濬益]]所執導<ref>{{cite web|title=New take on King Yeongjo and Prince Sado|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=3007874|accessdate=12 September 2015|date=14 August 2015|website=[[Korea_JoongAng_Daily|Korea JoongAng Daily]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150930124025/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=3007874|archive-date=2015-09-30|dead-url=no|last1=Jin|first1=Eun-soo}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=''The Throne'' filmmaker speaks highly of actor Song|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20150903001252|accessdate=12 September 2015|date=3 September 2015|website=[[The_Korea_Herald|The Korea Herald]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910002246/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20150903001252|archive-date=2015-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Movie tells timeless tale of father-son dispute|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=3009028|accessdate=12 September 2015|date=11 September 2015|website=[[Korea_JoongAng_Daily|Korea JoongAng Daily]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150930151532/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=3009028|archive-date=2015-09-30|dead-url=no|last1=Jin|first1=Eun-soo}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Herald Review: ''The Throne'' brings royal strife down to Earth|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20150916001125|accessdate=6 October 2015|date=16 September 2015|website=[[The_Korea_Herald|The Korea Herald]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916172832/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20150916001125|archive-date=2015-09-16|dead-url=no|last1=Won|first1=Ho-jung}}</ref>。電影講述[[朝鲜王朝|朝鲜王朝]][[莊獻世子|思-{}-悼世子]]，一位在27歲時被父親[[朝鮮英祖|英祖]]關進米櫃餓死的世子的一生<ref>{{cite web|title=Song Kang-ho joins Lee Joon-ik film|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2987312|accessdate=19 June 2014|date=3 April 2014|last=Kim|first=Hee-eun|website=[[Korea_JoongAng_Daily|Korea JoongAng Daily]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140402184459/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2987312|archive-date=2014-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=SONG Kang-ho Boards New LEE Joon-ik Film|url=http://www.koreanfilm.or.kr/jsp/news/news.jsp?mode=VIEW&seq=2989|accessdate=19 June 2014|date=9 April 2014|last=Conran|first=Pierce|work=Korean Film Biz Zone|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928122245/http://www.koreanfilm.or.kr/jsp/news/news.jsp?mode=VIEW&seq=2989|archive-date=2011-09-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Yoo Ah-in set for ''Sado'' role?|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2989075|accessdate=19 June 2014|date=14 May 2014|last=Kim|first=Hee-eun|website=[[Korea_Joongang_Daily|Korea Joongang Daily]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929195252/https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2989075|archive-date=2020-09-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Moon Geun Young, Yoo Ah In and Song Kang Ho Confirmed for Film ''Sado''|url=http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/66727/sado-finalizes-casting-with-moongeunyoung-and-yooahin|accessdate=19 June 2014|date=26 May 2014|last=Jeon|first=Su-mi|work=enewsWorld|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008163130/http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/66727/sado-finalizes-casting-with-moongeunyoung-and-yooahin|archive-date=2015-10-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Same role, different actors|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2014/11/201_163120.html|accessdate=9 November 2014|date=18 August 2014|last=Baek|first=Byung-yeul|website=[[The_Korea_Times|The Korea Times]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127114201/https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2014/11/201_163120.html|archive-date=2020-11-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影獲提名為[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡金像獎]][[奥斯卡最佳外语片奖|最佳外语片奖]]的候選電影<ref>{{cite web|title=Oscars: South Korea Submits ''The Throne'' for Foreign-Language Category|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-south-korea-submits-throne-820021|accessdate=3 September 2015|date=1 September 2015|last=Lee|first=Hyo-won|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017161407/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-south-korea-submits-throne-820021|archive-date=2019-10-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=''The Throne'' picked as Korean candidate for Academy Awards' foreign language film award|url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/news/2015/09/02/0200000000AEN20150902009700320.html|accessdate=2 September 2015|date=2 September 2015|website=[[Yonhap|Yonhap]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002111746/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/news/2015/09/02/0200000000AEN20150902009700320.html|archive-date=2015-10-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

